'''Stern Traders''' was a trading company owned by [[Roger Stern]]. It operated mainly from [[Da'Harrin Spaceport]] on [[Greyman's Planet]], where it handled the majority of operations in the spaceport so, when Roger Stern was captured for being a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] sympathizer, it caused the spaceport to go into chaos.

